      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Hard to knock I AM HELLBOUND (10) after racing parked but digging deep to record a third straight win at this venue last time out. Hasn't missed a place at this longer distance and while he gives away 20m at the handicap he won the last time he attempted a standing start. PESCO POLLO (7) hasn't raced since March but two trial wins suggest he has come back in good order. Has won fresh before and strikes at 50 per cent at this circuit and distance so looking for a strong return. SPEEDY LOVER (11) gives away 30m at the handicap but must be respected after enjoying the step up to this distance when finding winning form here last week. YOUR MAJESTY (8) has come from wide barriers for three wins and a placing behind I AM HELLBOUND in four starts this time in. Has won four of five tries at this distance so must be respected.",
